title: Snek or Treat! - Animated Short
description:
Happy Halloween! 
This is a little animated short film about two reptilian youths trick-or-treating on Halloween night. Their mysterious neighbor notices something very familiar about them...

Animation, illustration, backgrounds, sound editing, etc etc done by me.
